          </p>
          <p>
            The technology sector offers multiple entry points at this salary level. Junior web developers, IT helpdesk
            analysts, data entry specialists, and digital marketing assistants typically start in this range. The
            progression potential in technology is particularly strong because the demand for digital skills continues to
